{"tid":11191,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］同女神一齊睇你的名字...","createTime":"2016-11-29T08:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-09T01:19:34.000Z","uid":10337,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27d2737f183b9a095c4538c49ec0d3289f1ece4e","tid":11191,"uid":10337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n見到女神琴日朝早post左2張戲飛<br />\n係晏就去睇你的名字<br />\n<br />\n醒目嘅我即刻仆落戲院買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就買女神隔離果2個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1s5f63s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1s5f63s.jpg&h=003c8424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打算扮偶遇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁就到開場嘅時候<br />\n我就準時去到戲院買定爆谷汽水<br />\n坐定定等女神<br />\n<br />\n開場嘅時候女神同個男仔係左手邊入嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點撚知佢唔係坐我隔離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而係坐左手邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6D9B95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6D9B95.jpg&h=d19e15af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻起身<br />\n爆谷同汽水都唔記得拎<br />\n走去左邊女神隔離坐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BG4914V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBG4914V.jpg&h=163aea0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一坐低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：女神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁啱嘅 你又係睇呢場呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：好明顯啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你自己嚟睇呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔係呀 陪fd (然後就指住隔離個人）<br />\n<br />\n然後就坐埋d 拎定紙巾陣間俾女神<br />\n<br />\n睇睇下我覺得啲爆谷同汽水好晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是扮去廁所<br />\n過返右手邊拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點撚知女神係我去廁所嘅時候<br />\n同佢隔離個男仔調位喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/155751_039af676f8bc287a9d87b8d5944de476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F155751_039af676f8bc287a9d87b8d5944de476.jpg&h=c579e4cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 同女神你眼望我眼<br />\n場面好撚尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 之後我嗱嗱聲拎返啲嘢就返過去繼續睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當咩事都冇發生過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完場開燈<br />\n見到女神對眼腫晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔離個男仔輕輕咁攬住佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但主角不是我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正當我好唔開心嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：做咩唔帶紙巾比你個fd？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n擰轉身望一望<br />\n見到個暗瘡大肥婆 喊到湯豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左顯示我嘅gentlemen <br />\n我勉為其難第左張紙巾俾佢...<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企見到女神post左張咁嘅相...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9h65t8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9h65t8f.jpg&h=da289cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點算好...."},{"pid":"34f1b910b30d880f685e44be6bc734092fb45dd1","tid":11191,"uid":13696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:06:08.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"a17c94ca111d5f1e2c265385d4247cb82bfd468a","tid":11191,"uid":26971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68090b1bae2638cf38e797a6bcec55a8b9efffb0","tid":11191,"uid":31594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"你咩樣？"},{"pid":"eda767ece584c4ca1c030b0a7f5f23be51c3fe30","tid":11191,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"唉屌你都廢事<br />\n仲扮偶遇"},{"pid":"d5d65bc514d4db22afc9c28dbfb81e7d11971bb1","tid":11191,"uid":33445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00320032947338fe3bcd6810c3545a2ef2fb61c1","tid":11191,"uid":10337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咩樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女神話過我似一個踢波好勁既人<br />\n叫咩因黎c達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我就覺得自己似甘草米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8389f6408d161809595856e4d6073e7efb816fa1","tid":11191,"uid":10337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc